items.name: Character Design
items.description:
Character design is the process of creating and developing visual representations of characters for various forms of media, such as animation, video games, comics, and films.

In character design, artists consider various aspects to bring the character to life. This includes their appearance, personality, backstory, abilities, and role within the story. The goal is to create a visually compelling and memorable character that resonates with the audience.

Character designers often start by brainstorming and sketching different ideas, exploring variations in shapes, proportions, and features. They consider factors such as age, gender, body type, clothing, and accessories to convey the character's identity and characteristics.

Designers also pay attention to facial expressions, body language, and gestures to communicate emotions and personality traits. They consider color schemes, textures, and visual details that help define the character's world and story.

Character design can range from realistic and detailed to stylized and exaggerated, depending on the desired aesthetic and narrative tone. The design process may involve multiple iterations and feedback from creative teams to refine and enhance the character's visual appeal and storytelling potential.

Successful character design goes beyond just the visual aspect, aiming to create characters that are relatable, memorable, and able to connect with the audience on an emotional level. They play a crucial role in storytelling, contributing to the overall narrative and leaving a lasting impression.

Whether in animation, video games, or other media, well-crafted character design adds depth, personality, and visual interest to the creative work, enriching the audience's experience.

items.name: Hitotsuki & Hitotsuking (from Avataro Sentai Donbrothers)
items.description:
Before I go in and tackle the other Kamen Riders, I'm going to experiment with a larger dataset, since we're gonna be dealing with a ton more Kamen Riders.

Enter the Hitotsuki from Avataro Sentai Donbrothers. The dataset for the Hitotsuki are 50 images trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5, and they're perfect for this experiment because they all have the same lower body (barring a purple or red variation) with their top being different. I also included their giant versions, the Hitotsukings (also trained on SD 1.5 but with 27 images instead, omitting Resshaki and Kyukyuki due to them being CGI and potentially throwing off the whole dataset), as they have even more of a uniform fit to them.

In the end, I conclude that the Hitotsuki LoRA has no overcook, since it was able to produce a human without its face melting off (same holds true for Hitotsukings, but I wanted to give Monaking a monster face so I upped the weight for Hitotsuking). This proves that while the slow simmer method is still perfect for larger items, I'm a little nervous for the cook times, so the larger steps may need to necessitate a batch of 3 or 4, or I need to reduce the epochs to 15 for the sake of brevity and reducing the risk of overcook.

Also, the activation tags aren't programmed into the LoRA, but they seem to be what cause them to activate. I found you can use either one of them or both of them.

items.name: RFKTR's the last gathering MIX
items.description:
"THE LAST GATHERING

Standing on the last minutes of mankind, the end felt bittersweet, full of warm memories of the past. With each dimming light, they were saying goodbye to each other, looking in the face of a merciless future.

It was the last gathering around the bonfire, to tell the stories of humankind, sing and drink together whilst sitting on their whole lives fit into small compartments. They shared their stories, their laughter and tears blending together in the symphony of life. They sang songs, old and new, and raised their glasses in a final toast to the world that had been, and the world that would never be.

For some, it was a time of sorrow, for others, it was a time of peace. But as the last embers of the bonfire flickered and died, they knew that they had lived and loved, and that was all that mattered in the grand scheme of things. They were ready to face the darkness, together, as one."

===============================================

This model holds a special place in my heart, as I have spent a great deal of time training, mixing and refining it to create "The Last Gathering" - short story about acceptance of the inevitable and finding comfort in each other's company in the face of the end. It's not about desperation, but about bittersweet goodbye that feels warm and nostalgic. It's understanding that all the good things have to end.

Model has undergone countless changes and improvements, and I now feel that it is ready to be shared with others. Enjoy.

items.description:
This is a complete remake version of my Hwah Jah Jiangshi/Zombie 華甲-欢乐喜庆僵尸夜 - HuaJiaZombieV4-08 | Stable Diffusion LoRA | Civitai.

这是我的华甲僵尸的完全重制版。

Jiangshi(僵尸/殭屍) is a kind of Chinese undead monster, they are a little bit similar to western zombies but more powerful. Sometimes jiangshi is called Chinese vampire.

僵尸是一种中式亡灵，它们跟西方丧尸有点像但更强大，有时僵尸也被称为中国吸血鬼。

Read This!

Firstly I have to admit that several months ago I was totally a noob (now, too) who did not know how to arrange tags and what to delete. I even feel a bit ashamed and sorry when I see these four naive versions of Jwah Jah Jiangshi, actually they have problems such as:

  • It's hard to change or take off her clothes.

  • Her clothes is not stable enough. Sometimes the navel was exposed while sometimes the ofuda breast curtains were far from what it should be.

Now the there is the Remake Version:

  • NSFW Support√

  • Clothes Changing√

  • Multires Noise√

  • More Stable Clothes√

Well you might found there is more trigger words, but that is a must for flexibility：

  • "jiangshi" might bring Qing guanmao together, so you may not need 'qing guanmao".

  • Input "breast curtains" and "ofuda on nipples" together for a more stable result.

  • "no bra" is not necessary, it is for the case that some models like adding cloth and bra.

For short, "jiangshi, qing guanmao, china dress, breast curtains"

If Hawh Jah's hair is not black (for example when used with other lora or input too many tags for quality), just add "black hair".

用前先看！

首先我得承认几个月前我是个纯菜鸡（现在也菜），不知道怎么调整tag和删哪些tag。前几个版本的华甲是很不成熟的作品，现在看来真是有点羞耻，它们包括但不限于以下问题：

  • 衣服难脱和更换

  • 衣服不够稳定，有时露了肚脐，胸口的符咒并不稳定，有时候会加布料。

现在有了重做版Remake Version:

  • 可以涩涩√

  • 可以换装√

  • 金字塔噪声√

  • 更稳定的衣服√

不过你可能会发现哎触发词变多了，但是这是为了灵活性所必须的：

  • "jiangshi" 可能自带清官帽，所以你或许不用输入“qing guanmao”。

  • 同时输入"breast curtains" 和 "ofuda on nipples" 以获得更稳定的效果。

  • "no bra" 不是必要的，它主要用以应对一些模型喜欢加布料和胸罩的情况。

想要简单点的触发词直接 "jiangshi, qing guanmao, china dress, breast curtains"这几个就够了。

如果华甲的头发不黑了 (比如跟其他lora叠加使用或者加了太多质量词), 请自行添加 "black hair"。
